package.description:
This extension supports label for following products .&#13;
&#13;
1) New Arrivals Products.&#13;
2) Best Sellers Products.&#13;
3) Product On Sale (To apply this label apply special price while adding product).&#13;
4) Most Reviewed Products.&#13;
Product Ribbon can displayed dynamically on the Product Listing and Detailed View page. This Magento Extension will allow your main image product to be displayed with a nice Ribbon on sales,new,best seller and top rated product.&#13;
eature&#13;
1) Apply attractive ribbon for on sales, new, best selling and top rated products.&#13;
2) Show multiple ribbons per product image.&#13;
3) Limit ribbons displaying based on conditions.&#13;
4) Upload  ribbon exactly the way you want. &#13;
5) The module supports to display in many modes.&#13;
6) Ribbon can be displayed anywhere in the catalog, search and product view&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
Other Feature &#13;
1) Administrator can Add/ Edit/ Delete the ribbons for the products in the website.&#13;
2) Administrator can manage the positioning of the ribbons to the product image.&#13;
Top - Left ,Top – Right,Bottom – Left,Bottom - Right.&#13;
3) Administrator can also manage the display settings for the ribbons to the product images&#13;
Product category listing page - Yes/ No&#13;
Product detailed view product gallery - Yes/ No&#13;
4) Admin Panel can easily manage the product labels style for listing and view page.&#13;
5)  “New” Ribbon to Newly Added products(sales,new,best seller and top rated ) automatically.&#13;
6) Administrator can also Enable/Disable the ribbon images added.&#13;
7) Easy customizable - no coding!&#13;
Installation&#13;
- Easy integration, no installation or setup is necessary on the server. All you have to do is upload your files.&#13;
